Description

app/ – Contains all screens and navigation

assets/ – Application images and icons

constants/ – Global constants like theme colors

mocks/ – Sample data used during development

types/ – TypeScript interfaces for the application

configuration files – Expo, TypeScript, Metro, and ESLint settings

Key Screens
Role Selection Screen

Allows users to choose their role in the system.

Home Screen

Displays restaurants with available meals.

Restaurant Details

Shows meal descriptions, tags, allergens, and quantities.

Map Screen

Displays restaurant locations and pickup logistics.

Restaurant Sign In

Allows restaurants to manage food donations.

